OL,6,
OL,7,GWhat do viewers in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Gcall the third channel? ITV? ITV1? UTV?
OL,9,GThe UTV? Ulster Television?
OL,11,
OL,12,FThe name ITV plc thinks you should use
OL,13,Fis not at all clear even if the station
OL,14,Fbranding is now strong and explicit.
OL,16,
OL,17,FWith the revamp of ITV 1, visually
OL,18,FUTV's brand seems to have reached its
OL,19,Ffinal destination.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
OL,22,                                   G1/9
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
