OL,6,
OL,7,FTrails now follow the standard ITV 1
OL,8,Fformat. 1s fly over the screen as the
OL,9,Ftrail transitions to the endboard. Then
OL,10,Fat the very end the ITV 1 logo wipes
OL,11,Fon.
OL,13,
OL,14,FUTV is effectively a hallmark  a
OL,15,Ftrusted brand which brings together the
OL,16,Flocal output.
OL,18,
OL,19,FVisually there is no doubt the channel
OL,20,Fname is ITV 1  trails, idents and the
OL,21,FDOG all highlight the name.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
