OL,6,
OL,7,FBefore it was just about conceivable
OL,8,Fthe ITV name (left out of local promos)
OL,9,Fwas just the old generic name for the
OL,10,Fnetwork.
OL,12,
OL,13,FBut orally the name is less clear.
OL,14,FAnnouncements before local programmes
OL,15,Frarely, if ever, give a name.
OL,17,
OL,18,FBut trails still tend to end with the
OL,19,Fwords "on UTV"  even with the ITV 1
OL,20,Fname on screen.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
