OL,6,
OL,7,FSimilarly the EPG still refers solely
OL,8,Fto UTV.
OL,10,
OL,11,FITV has always been very hesitant to be
OL,12,Fseen as downgrading the UTV brand. It
OL,13,Fis, of course, a name which goes back
OL,14,Fmany years.
OL,16,
OL,17,FBut we're at the point where the
OL,18,Fremaining hesitancy seems hard to
OL,19,Fjustify.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
