OL,6,
OL,7,FThe other mystery concerns the EPG
OL,8,Fname.
OL,10,
OL,11,FIn English regions the name is simply
OL,12,F"ITV 1". Wales and the Scottish part of
OL,13,Fthe Border region are afforded an
OL,14,Fappropriate suffix.
OL,16,
OL,17,FBut the EPG name in Northern Ireland
OL,18,Fremains UTV alone.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
