OL,6,
OL,7,FTake one step back. This risks being
OL,8,Fconfusing to someone with no prior
OL,9,Fknowledge. Either the channel is ITV 1
OL,10,For UTV.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe obvious thing to do is to change
OL,14,Fthe EPG name to "ITV 1 UTV"
OL,16,
OL,17,FNeither of these two changes would
OL,18,Fcause the sky to fall in but it would
OL,19,Fmake the channel name definitive.
OL,3,CDoes UTV have a future as an ITV 1
OL,4,Csub-brand?
