OL,6,
OL,7,FThe UTV name appears to have a future
OL,8,Fas a trusted sub-brand under the ITV 1
OL,9,Fmasterbrand. A hallmark on local
OL,10,Foutput.
OL,12,
OL,13,FI would be surprised if UTV Live does
OL,14,Fnot adopt explicit ITV News branding at
OL,15,Fsome point but I would also be shocked
OL,16,Fif the name changed unless there was a
OL,17,Fwider shake-up across the network. It's
OL,18,Fno "worse" than ITV News Granada
OL,19,FReports or ITV News Meridian.
